<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idab5a79c4-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5" identifier="/us/usc/t10/s9018"><num value="9018">§ 9018.</num><heading> Administrative Assistant</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Secretary of the Air Force may appoint an Administrative Assistant in the Office of the Secretary of the Air Force. The Administrative Assistant shall perform such duties as the Secretary may prescribe.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idab5a79c5-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5">(Added <ref href="/us/pl/99/433/tV/s521/a/5">Pub. L. 99–433, title V, § 521(a)(5)</ref>, <date date="1986-10-01">Oct. 1, 1986</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/100/1059">100 Stat. 1059</ref>, § 8018; renumbered § 9018, <ref href="/us/pl/115/232/dA/tVIII/s806/c">Pub. L. 115–232, div. A, title VIII, § 806(c)</ref>, <date date="2018-08-13">Aug. 13, 2018</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/132/1833">132 Stat. 1833</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="idab5a79c6-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5">
