<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="amendments" id="idab5a79c8-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Amendments</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">2018—<ref href="/us/pl/115/232">Pub. L. 115–232</ref> renumbered <ref href="/us/usc/t10/s8018">section 8018 of this title</ref> as this section.</p>
